<br>
President Clinton: Steals small items from the White House as he leaves office.  Certainly petty theft is not the philosophy of all Americans.  Cheats on his wife - certainly not a philosophy of all Americans either.<br>
<br>
Enron and WorldCom: One can hardly say doctoring the books or tampering with evidence is a philosophy for all Enron or WorldCom employees now.<br>
